  "reference_number": "RUS1363",
  "remarks": "\nColonel General Andrey SERDYUKOV is the Commander of the Airborne Forces of the Russian Federation. The Russian Airborne Forces have been heavily involved in the ongoing invasion of Ukraine by Russia, including an aerial assault on the city of Kharkiv. As the Airborne Supreme Commander, Colonel General SERDYUKOV has oversight of and directs the actions of the Russian Airborne Forces. \nThere are therefore reasonable grounds to suspect that SERDYUKOV is an involved person, who is responsible for, engages in, provides support for, or promotes any policy or action which destabilises Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
